Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.32,0:00:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯塔尔那家伙 以为自己去了安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法骑士团50人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}（布洛福斯邸 寝室）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个跳梁小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟皇子殿下作对还以为能赢 真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.47,0:00:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个色狼黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准用那种色迷迷的眼神看姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.31,0:00:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难过…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是那么宠伊莉丝啊 菲莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.41,0:00:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作要认真完成才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这种人活命的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对艾利斯家有害无益吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背后黑幕是皇子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说席恩也是皇子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利斯家只侍奉罗兰德之王 真正的王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.72,0:01:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说王？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须确认一下席恩是否配得上当王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他以魔法骑士团50人为敌 能不能活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.17,0:01:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩并不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.94,0:01:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 他不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他身上有某种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.82,0:01:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你与席恩相遇 结果救了他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点也不觉得有趣

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（op）



Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,500)}{\fs40}艾斯塔布尔国境附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各班 开始准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先确保水源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空闲的人去搭帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,500)}{\fs40}复写眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去提水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别绊着了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也去帮忙搭帐篷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦 不干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 姬珐 你也说他两句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊我肚子不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我没在听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬珐 那个万年懒惰男不肯帮忙搭帐篷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳只听姬珐的话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子对姬珐做了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看她都不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家真是迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在打仗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到心爱的人会有个什么三长两短的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会变得忧郁起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说 出兵之前姬珐对你说过什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…最害怕的就是莱纳会死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去提水了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去林子里拾点柴禾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帐篷怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你们留守了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是个大好天气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…我就睡个午觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳 和我一起…逃走好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 和我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟随席恩了 和我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是不应该的 但我还是喜欢上了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳你…不喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啦 姬珐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候还开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对 我果然是得不到任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我还是不希望莱纳死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没能保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:06:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文 寄宿沉眠于大气中的光之精兽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔伊尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对我们艾斯塔布尔魔法骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为你们能逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布尔国发动敌袭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身着红色甲胄的骑士接连不断地…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色甲胄？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布尔的魔法骑士团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃进森林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重整队形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…塔伊尔被…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是去提水的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还说跟着席恩就绝对安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬珐怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵分两路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 珐露先走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这里断后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许还有同伴幸存
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括姬珐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说要去救他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实不大可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗兰德的小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逃就太没劲了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文 寄宿沉眠于大气中的恶意之精兽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那种魔法来加速的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文 寄宿沉眠于大气中的恶意之精兽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…但是你…刚才的魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明知道的 我不想用的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 为何会用我们的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是复写眼持有者？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说会带来灾厄的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾…献上契约之文 释放舞动于天空中…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 别用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文 释放舞动于天空中的光之魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你早点使用这种力量 大家都不用死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人只有三个才能过关的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我都七年没用过这能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们看了场好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复写眼倒挺稀奇 这怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再害怕点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给点乐子 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有复写眼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你看点好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物 搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着的就剩那两人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其余的全杀光了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了这话还这么冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 便如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去释放
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到眼中一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部消失为止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的分子将化作砂砾消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神灵 恶魔 勇者 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝等将如何称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子 赐你一死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文 释放覆盖宇宙的精灵之力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解析存在　将之解除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起源（α）即破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾不创造任何事物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惠泽 不拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:12:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅消除 回归纯白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溃灭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量…契约不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 眼睛…要闭上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要闭上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要闭上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳 喂 听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}罗兰德帝国 首都
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,500)}{\fs40}罗兰德 王立军事特殊学院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖待在学院里被养着就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬珐…她还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早进了这里的牢房了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到她还会跑回原处来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几年前查获一批间谍时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她姐姐被处死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下她和妹妹接受了我国的再教育
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹为了表示对我国的忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接说当人质比较快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也真是个傻女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹早就被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是个人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯塔尔那小子活下来就没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正目标是他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此那些大人们可是把我们骂个狗血淋头 你小子能明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就是为了发牢骚 才把我抓来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么口气 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那下有点略痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话 你瞧不起我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧不起人的是你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可从来都是被人瞧不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚够了没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我倒下之前快关我进牢房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王说 把你关进牢房之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以实现你一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在倒是可以麻烦你们给我止血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,500)}{\fs40}罗兰德 看守所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 姬珐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再睡下去成绩要退步了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该从哪里说起好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好麻烦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说麻烦就一拳打飞你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打别打头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚止的血又会飙出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那伤是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管这伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些事想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬珐的妹妹已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说很久以前就被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳你怎么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是罗兰德的爪牙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想听 我不想听妹妹的死讯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是从你的口中说出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道一切还在心里嘲笑我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还说我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑我是个笨女人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹或许已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也隐隐约约察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要打仗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们的领地什么的 我可是毫无兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我早说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午睡最好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔伊尔 托尼 珐露真是白白送死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是有干劲的人才会发动战争吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把没干劲的人都卷进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那没干劲的人该怎么做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没像席恩那样 想过要改变国家什么的麻烦事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:18:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用午睡 不用伤害任何人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底哪里才有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 姬珐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是说了什么奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 姬珐 你来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝贺你出狱 姬珐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后祝贺我入狱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的愿望这算是了了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了 买卖成交
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳·琉特入狱的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是释放姬珐·诺尔兹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以和军部直接讨价还价的大坏蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事情别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳你为什么要为我做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出卖了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家都被杀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人的不是人 是怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家也是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲望是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我也是…怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过姬珐是人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在这里当个午睡王国的国王君临天下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬珐就在外面…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白自己为什么会喜欢莱纳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你没有干劲到完全不需要戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人安心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本是这样想的 但错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是因为你很善良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳 你不是什么怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以打包票
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一定会把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:19:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为要窒息了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那伤是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了点小事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻的吗 听说你是主动入狱的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 要会面还真费了我一番功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是何必呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是关我的地方 从学校换成监狱罢了

Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我在北侧森林里放匹马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做你会被怀疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还没胆量把战争英雄关进监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:21:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过能成为拖英雄下水的契机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我也经历过不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地不少哦 想让你不幸的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是唯一的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后不保证还能和你见面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我也没信心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴死去 发生战争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在还当不上王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是我的过失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很麻烦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 就算这次顺利过关了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后还不知会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳 你这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在这里悠闲地睡午觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡午觉能成什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡睡午觉 然后再想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩大人您该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.47,0:21:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就再被饲养一阵了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里带三餐还让午睡 够爽的了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.28,0:22:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 下次见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下定了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去一切的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.55,0:22:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没什么好犹豫的了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳 我一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你早点使用这种力量 大家都不用死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是战争不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要打仗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.70,0:22:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关灯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:22:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是发生了不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.97,0:23:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天不会再有这么多事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今后还有很多时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.82,0:23:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力啊加油什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要睡着就不会发生任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要这样就满足了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}莱纳·报告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.69,0:23:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢…
